title: Kingsland. Healthy Vegan Restaurant
description: Kingsland's menu features a range of vegetables, tofu, soy seafood and soy meat dishes, some crunchy entrees and ice cream desserts. Dishes are served with more salad and vegetables. Live music and karaoke occasionally, suitable for party function up to 70 persons. High chairs provided for children. Located in Canberra Chinatown area, under current ownership since Apr 2010.
streetAddress: Shop 5 Dickson Plaza, 67-69 Woolley St, Dickson
